                  <decoDesc>
                     <summary>On the S face there are seven seperate mosaics. The main one is in the form of a Greek cross with a circular centre, which has a chi-rho on it. The arms of the cross have a symmetrical geometric design. At three points of the cross there are small round mosaics, again with a geometric design. On the main shaft of the stone there is a diamond mosaic, followed by a small Greek cross, followed by another diamond. All have geometric designs. All the mosaics are in colour.</summary>
